                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-683-18680817 t18680817-683-punishment-36"></join>
                     <hi rend="italic">Twelve Months' Imprisonment, to commence at the expiration of the former sentence</hi>
                  </rs>.</p>
